-------------zm_breakable_teeter_totter_b1-------------
zm_breakable_teeter_totter_b1 brought to you by the Official Zombie Mod Studio 
This is somewhat of a remake of breakfloorzm 

The original map breakfloowzm was released last night when I got the idea to make a teeter totter map with a breakable floor. I ask grey echo if I could remake the map and this is what I came up with

zm_breakable_teeter_totter_b1
This map is based off of a popular glass map called break floor but it has been redesigned textured and optimized for zombie mod on top of that I added a swinging teeter totter on the very top of a tower zombie must first break the lower supports to allow the players to sway out of control. Making it easier for zombie to kill someone. The first few minutes of the round are crucial and will decide the faith of the humans.  If there are to many people on one side of the tower floor the himian will crash down to there deaths 

I will figure out how to make a demo of this 

-------------------------------------------
Map specs
-------------------------------------------
-Stylish De_dust theme.
- teleport at the bottom of the pit so users are returned to the top if they fall
- Maximum optimization for the least amount of FPS loss and lag possible.
-Real time lighting 
-3d skybox
-32spawn points
-Custom phys override (will fix lag issues and stop glitches on the map)
-Cool teeter Totter 
-------------------------------------------
updates
-------------------------------------------
-Fixed  Teleport
-------------------------------------------
